(883, '64f7a29641de0', 'What we cannot see, parental violence', '2023-09-05 22:46:05', '', 3, 'Child abuse is a global problem without social, racial, and ethnic boundaries and can involve adults and children because the perpetrators of abuse may be intentional or unintentional and can include acts of omission such as neglect, and/or commission such as abuse. Case report: A 19-year-old female was physically and emotionally abused by her father causing emotional trauma to her. She had several suicidal attempts and was diagnosed with a major depression disorder (MDD) due to the physical and emotional abuse of her father and other family members. Managed with antidepressants, psychotherapy, and weekly cognitive behavioral therapeutic sessions. Coming into the psychiatric sector at this stage might provide the patient and her siblings the support they need and avert serious health problems for them. Counseling services for children and caregivers should form part of the management regime.', '', '', '', 389, 'Child abuse, Depression, Suicide, Homicide, Violence', 0, 0, 0, '2023-09-05 22:46:05', 0, 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0),
(884, '6517374fcb96f', 'Molecular Identification and Phylogenic Tree of Ascaris spp. Isolated from Child Stools at Erbil province ', '2023-09-29 20:47:08', '', 1, 'Human infections with Ascaris species have been observed in most parts of Iraq. The stool samples were collected from rural residences, and genomic DNA was extracted from each case. The ITS1-rDNA region was amplified using PCR, and the results were sequenced. Among 50 children, 9 (18%) were found to be infected. Phylogenetic analysis demonstrated that each Ascaris lumbricoides (A. lumbricoides) under the accession number (ON678065, ON678066, ON678067 and ON678068) were grouped together with reference sequences of A. lumbricoides uploaded to the GenBank database (MK849920), and the similarity in the current study ranged from 99.64% to 100% for all species. ', '', '', '', 391, 'Ascarids, Sequence analysis, Phytogenic relationships ', 0, 0, 0, '2023-09-29 20:47:08', 0, 0, 5, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0),
